reviews.comment: Didn\'t like it at first.  But once I figured it out,  I couldn\'t put it down.  I\'d like to be able to vote on the online gallery  submissions.  Some people did really outstanding work.\tLove the app.

reviews.title: Turns awful artists into renaissance masters
reviews.comment: I am by no means artistically adept. This amazing app makes it possible for me to create art I never would be able to, otherwise.
